						<h4>Inspiration</h4>
						<p>BB Tapes is an E-Commerce company that sells physical copies of Boom Bap Music. From timeless albums to undiscovered artist mixtapes, we have you covered.
                            Boom Bap is a sub-genre of Hip Hop that has been popular since Hip Hop’s very inception in the late 70s. Most Boom Bap fans enjoy the nostalgic feeling of unwrapping a new CD and/or unboxing a new Cassette as opposed to downloading an entire album. BB Tapes aims to be the main online supplier of physical Boom Bap music worldwide.</p>
